description:
Israel criticized and murmured against Gods health message. Has Gods Adventist health message to the remnant met a similar fate? Walter Veith looks at the physical and spiritual implications of rejecting Gods health message. This lecture explores Gods great end-time health message as it is written into the lives of ancient Israel and its prophets such as Daniel and John the Baptist, who serve as typical Elijahs. 

As God tried to lead the children of Israel back to Himself, so God will do the same for antitypical Israel. Learn how rejecting the health message today will lead to the same results ancient Israel experienced.

http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/media/1178/1006-nothing-but-this-manna/

Discover more: http://amazingdiscoveries.org/
